==Korean==
===Noun===
'''버클''' (''beokeul'') 
# (''loanword'') [[buckle]] 

====Etymology====
* Middle English [[bocle]] "buckle, boss of a shield"
* Middle English [[bokelen]] "to arch the body" 
* Old French [[bocler]] "to bulge, curl"
* Latin [[buccula]] "cheek strap of a helmet", diminutive of [[bucca]] "cheek"

